    "description": "<h3>BOARDS</h3><p>A pair of special boots with wheels on the bottom, allowing the wearer to skate upon the ground.</p><p>While you have <strong>Blades</strong> equipped, you enter <strong>conflict scenes</strong> where you were the leader or succeeded your <strong>Support</strong> Check, with two sections of your Momentum Clock filled. The following <strong>tricks</strong> are known based on what benefits you have in this wheel. You must have a <strong>Blades</strong> equipped to use these <strong>tricks</strong>.</p><p>-</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"520\"><p><strong>Trick</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Momentum</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"520\"><p><strong>BASIC: Thorn Dagger Spin</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>-2</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Make two <strong>free attacks</strong>. These attacks replace their <strong>HR</strong> with your <strong>MV</strong>.</p><p>-</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"520\"><p><strong>Trick</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Momentum</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"520\"><p><strong>BASIC: Thorn Dagger Spin</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>-1</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Choose an ally you can see. They gain a bonus equal to your current <strong>HV</strong> to their next check.</p><p>-</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"520\"><p><strong>Trick</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Momentum</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"520\"><p><strong>BASIC: Thorn Dagger Spin</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>-1</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Every ally of your choice that you can see recovers HP and MP equal to 2 × <strong>MV</strong>. You can immediately use another (different) <strong>trick.</strong></p><p>-</p>",
